   "source": [
    "Greedy bandit learner\n",
    "- running independently per participant\n",
    "\n",
    "- each arm for each participant has true mean reward\n",
    "- learn by averaging "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 180,
   "id": "4167ee09-c94e-4c92-b9d6-dea11f1dda67",
